- https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AIRFLOW-118

The change is backward-compatible in cases where the `num_shards` is already set and that setting is still honored. But for cases where `num_shards` is not set, the default behavior will be using `targetPartitionSize` with the default parameter coming from http://druid.io/docs/latest/ingestion/batch-ingestion.html

